thread.title: Julie Gray

author: Julie Gray
title: Julie Gray
text: Really good overall experience and infact got upgraded twice by the car rental companies. Would recommend though that you do'nt take out the insurance that is prompted by you when booking through this site because each of the car rental companies offers their own. If you had taken it out like I had and anything happened, I would have had to pay the excess which is around $4k+ and then claim it back by a third party. Whereas if you take from the car rental companies direct they don't make you do that. Apart from that, all great experience.
